{"tid":2083580,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"腰痛腳痛圍爐區","createTime":"2020-06-29T00:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T18:37:24.000Z","uid":315236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"482e4dd6ab792126db1ca125294762a556f7f98a","tid":2083580,"uid":315236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:17:34.000Z","msg":"痛咗半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次痛嘅時候，拖咗2個月先睇醫生<br />\n醫生話我肌肉缺乏訓練，當時隻腳平躺係上到80度，是但比咗啲止痛藥我同叫我做運動。<br />\n<br />\n結果做完佢叫我做啲運動越做越痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過多2個月，有一日痛到坐唔到係到食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂唔順去危症，醫生話我背脊骨直咗壓住神經線所以痛+麻痺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />轉介去骨科，要等到9月先有期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當時隻腳都仲上到70度<br />\n<br />\n最近呢個月，懷疑自己仲有埋椎間盤突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />忽然有一日瞓醒覺痛到喊咗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係好郁到，發現隻腳伸直上唔到40度，得20幾30度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府又無期，有人介紹咗去睇針灸，針完個下有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過咗一日又開始痛翻<br />\n<br />\n依家放暑假，工又返唔到，想坐係到溫下書又坐唔到，好似條廢柴咁日日要瞓向床到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得自己好無用"},{"pid":"9aa8d2ca3e0198c7827ce0afca8564e37df906ad","tid":2083580,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:18:25.000Z","msg":"睇私家啦師兄，有無買保險"},{"pid":"c2799bacf6925714235b52b77ac2c0c31bc2d3db","tid":2083580,"uid":315236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aa8d2ca3e0198c7827ce0afca8564e37df906ad","tid":2083580,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:18:25.000Z","msg":"睇私家啦師兄，有無買保險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:19:42.000Z","msg":"有買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但怕claim唔足<br />\n<br />\nbtw我係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e5f42ca00112089551aa676320299ff693133f","tid":2083580,"uid":139473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:21:59.000Z","msg":"做yoga拉筋啦<br />\nBtw我跑完跑右腳踭都會痛，諗會唔會扁平足<br />\n我可以幫人按摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ae3f226cc31778f9a75e83aebacdeaa0c3d82e","tid":2083580,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2799bacf6925714235b52b77ac2c0c31bc2d3db","tid":2083580,"uid":315236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aa8d2ca3e0198c7827ce0afca8564e37df906ad","tid":2083580,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:18:25.000Z","msg":"睇私家啦師兄，有無買保險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:19:42.000Z","msg":"有買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但怕claim唔足<br />\n<br />\nbtw我係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:22:39.000Z","msg":"健康&gt;&gt;&gt;錢<br />\n同埋你問下agent先啦，照下MRI<br />\n<br />\n短期要止痛藥，中長期要物理治療果D"},{"pid":"c6a3f82d27e89cc3f8f555c55700597dc5012c46","tid":2083580,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"